# Implementation Plan - Bible Text Cleanup & Memo Feature

## Goal Description
1.  **Clean up Bible Text:** Remove the HTML entity `&#x27;` occurring in the Bible text on [BiblePage.jsx](file:///c:/Users/admin/.gemini/%EB%82%98%EC%9D%98%20%EC%82%AC%EB%9E%91%ED%95%98%EB%8A%94%20%EC%B1%85/src/pages/BiblePage.jsx).
2.  **Add Memo Feature:** Add a link on the Home Page (under Prayer) to a new Memo Page. The Memo Page will support adding memos with checkboxes/toggles and will implement pagination (5 items per page).

## User Review Required
-   **Persistence:** I will assume local storage or `DataContext` for now unless a backend is explicitly required for this new feature, consistent with recent "Server-Side Persistence" work. I'll check `DataContext` to see if it's already set up for general data.

